ae47bf%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223570%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAs%20a%20longtime%20local%2C%20I%20think%20the%20NYC%20commuter%20ferry%20is%20the%20best%20way%20to%20sightsee%20in%20the%20city.%3Cp%3EJohn%20Penney%2FShutterstock%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EI%20lived%20in%20New%20York%20for%2020%20years%20and%20think%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-public-transportation-new-york-city-ferry-opinion-2023-8%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ENYC%20commuter%20ferry%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20the%20best%20way%20to%20see%20the%20city.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EA%20%244.50%20ticket%20provides%20iconic%20skyline%20views%20and%20a%20close-up%20look%20at%20NYC's%20famous%20bridges.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThere's%20also%20a%20bar%20on%20board%20that%20offers%20a%20selection%20of%20drinks%20and%20snacks%20to%20enjoy%20on%20the%20journey.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EI%20lived%20in%20New%20York%20for%2020%20years%2C%20and%20whenever%20family%20or%20friends%20came%20to%20visit%2C%20one%20of%20my%20favorite%20ways%20to%20show%20off%20the%20city%20was%20from%20the%20water.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20there%20are%20several%20operators%20that%20offer%20touristy%20boat%20tours%2C%20depending%20on%20your%20budget%20and%20schedule%2C%20they%20can%20be%20expensive%20and%20time-consuming.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20a%20quicker%2C%20more%20affordable%20experience%2C%20I%20always%20recommend%20the%20NYC%20commuter%20ferry%20that%20runs%20along%20the%20East%20River.%20It's%20a%20terrific%20way%20to%20enjoy%20the%20views%20and%20take%20in%20some%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flocal-reveals-best-things-to-see-nyc-2018-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eclassic%20NYC%20sights%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20for%20just%20%244.50.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20the%20company%2C%20NYC%20Ferry%2C%20offers%20several%20different%20routes%20along%20the%20East%20River%2C%20one%20of%20my%20favorites%20for%20sightseeing%20is%20the%20Astoria%20line.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20why%20I%20think%20it's%20the%20best%20way%20to%20see%20the%20city.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EA%20trip%20on%20the%20Astoria%20line%20takes%20less%20than%20an%20hour.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20NYC%20Ferry%20sign%20indicating%20the%20Astoria%20to%20Wall%20Street%20route.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6883c80a85e81483682eb5cf%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ECarmenRM%2FShutterstock%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Astoria%20line%20begins%20at%20East%2090th%20Street%20on%20the%20Upper%20East%20Side%20of%20Manhattan%20and%20runs%20all%20the%20way%20to%20its%20final%20stop%20at%20Wall%20Street.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20journey%20takes%20about%2050%20minutes%20and%20includes%20scenic%20stops%20in%20Queens%2C%20Manhattan%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-ways-i-use-space-and-decorate-nyc-rental-2022-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EBrooklyn%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20trip%20can%20also%20be%20done%20in%20reverse%2C%20depending%20on%20what's%20next%20on%20your%20itinerary%20and%20where%20you%20want%20to%20end%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ETickets%20can%20be%20purchased%20on%20an%20app%20or%20at%20ticket%20machines.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224677%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20walkway%20boarding%20the%20NYC%20Ferry%2C%20with%20a%20woman%20turning%20around%20and%20smiling.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6883c9b23d5881a51c1e0814%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223508%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EPamela%20Vachon%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20ferries%20run%20on%20a%20schedule%20and%20depart%20once%20or%20twice%20an%20hour%2C%20depending%20on%20the%20time%20of%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20never%20found%20them%20to%20be%20too%20cr