-2018-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EOprah%20Winfrey%3C%2Fa%3E%20shared%20one%20of%20her%20famous%20nuggets%20of%20wisdom%3A%20%26quot%3BIt's%20great%20to%20have%20a%20private%20jet%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%20at%20Duke%20University's%202009%20commencement.%20%26quot%3BAnyone%20that%20tells%20you%20that%20having%20your%20own%20private%20jet%20isn't%20great%20is%20lying%20to%20you.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20she%20did%20leave%20out%20one%20detail%3A%20Having%20a%20private%20jet%20is%20expensive%20%E2%80%94%20%3Cem%3Ereally%20%3C%2Fem%3Eexpensive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECosts%20such%20as%20crew%2C%20custom%20features%2C%20and%20maintenance%20can%20add%20to%20the%20already%20hefty%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcosts-of-owning-private-jet-not-for-millionaires-2019-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eprice%20tag%20of%20purchasing%20a%20private%20plane%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20companies%20that%20manage%20these%20and%20charter%20fleets%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20a%20lot%20that%20goes%20into%20owning%20an%20airplane%2C%20a%20lot%20of%20expenses%20that%20aren't%20on%20the%20surface%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Jamie%20Walker%2C%20the%20executive%20chairman%20of%20jet%20management%20company%20Jet%20Linx.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20the%20most%20popular%20private%20jet%20models%20%E2%80%94%20the%20Bombardier%20Challenger%20300%20and%20350%2C%20the%20Embraer%20Phenom%20300%2C%20the%20Cessna%20Citation%20XLS%2B%2C%20and%20the%20Gulfstream%20G550%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%E2%80%94%20cost%20between%20%249.5%20million%20and%20%2433%20million%20brand%20new%2C%20Walker%20estimated.%20The%20cost%20fluctuates%20by%20model.%20But%20even%20when%20purchased%20used%2C%20many%20list%20for%20sale%20for%20eight%20figures.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20not%20including%20customization%2C%20which%20is%20%26quot%3Bwhere%20things%20get%20fun%2C%26quot%3B%20Walker%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESee%3A%20Paris%20Hilton's%20%26quot%3BSlivAir%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20Gulfstream%20G450%20with%20a%20Barbie%20pink%20paint%20job%20and%20%26quot%3BThat's%20Hot%26quot%3B%20written%20on%20a%20wing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe've%20seen%20clients%20spend%20anywhere%20from%20a%20few%20hundred%20thousand%20to%20several%20million%20on%20customizations%2C%26quot%3B%20Walker%20said%2C%20who%20compared%20it%20to%20%26quot%3Bbuilding%20a%20luxury%20home.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInterior%20upgrades%20like%20custom%20cabinetry%20and%20headrests%20imprinted%20with%20logos%20start%20at%20about%20%2465%2C000.%20Premium%20woodwork%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhermes-became-ultimate-status-symbol-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EHerm%C3%A8s%20leather%3C%2Fa%3E%20seats%20can%20exceed%20%241%20million.%20WiFi%20from%20Starlink%20or%20L5%20can%20cost%20between%20%24120%2C000%20and%20%24450%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22da6ff217-db8d-4211-9dd6-a14e12fa8a70%5C%22%3EA%20private%20jet%20can%20cost%20more%20than%20%241%20million%20a%20year%20to%20run%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20a%20jet%20is%20delivered%2C%20the%20costs%20of%20operating%20it%20start%20to%20add%20up.%C2%A0Leona%20Qi%2C%20the%20president%20of%20the%20US%20division%20of%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftaylor-swift-vistajet-private-jet-global-7500-jet-lag-tips-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Echarter%20firm%20VistaJet%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20estimated%20that%C2%A0it%20typically%20costs%20more%20than%20%241%20million%20a%20year%20to%20run%20a%20single%20jet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMembers%20of%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fprivate-jet-pilot-describes-job-surprising-things-2023-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eprivate%20jet's%20crew%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20at%20least%20two%20pilots%2C%20sometimes%20an%20air%20host%20%E2%80%94%20are%20typically%20considered%20full-time%20employees.%20Each%20can%20earn%20between%20%24150%2C000%20and%20%24400%2C000%20a%20year.%20They%20also%20have%20to%20be%20properly%20certified%2C%20trained%2C%20and%20insured%2C%20at%20the%20owner's%20cost.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20some%20jet%20maintenance%20is%20scheduled%20%E2%80%94%20much%20like%20a%20car's%2C%20it's%20based%20on%20mileage%20and%20crew%20%E2%80%94%20unexpected%20fixes%20can%20leave%20an%20unlucky%20owner%20seven%20figures%20in%20the%20red%20in%20a%20bad%20year.%20An%20engine%20overhaul%2C%20for%20example%2C%20can%20cost%20as%20much%20as%20%241.5%20million%20per%20engine%2C%20Walker%20estimated%20(and%20most%20jets%20have%20two).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%20there's%20a%20hangar.%20A%20parking%20spot%20in%20New%20York%20or%20Miami%20can%20cost%20as%20much%20as%20%24450%2C000%20a%20year%2C%20significantly%20more%20than%20one%20in%20smaller%20cities%20like%20Omaha%20or%20St.%20Louis.%20Fuel%20can%20make%20up%20about%20one-third%20of%20all%20ownership%20costs%2C%20Walker%20said.%20And%20most%20private%20jet%20owners%20hire%20a%20company%20to%20manage%20it%20all.%20Jet%20Linx%20said%20it%20charges%20between%20%247%2C000%20and%20%2412%2C000%20a%20month%20for%20its%20management%20services.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2257fb6de0-c1bf-41bd-875e-db963e303434%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ETo%20charter%20or%20not%20to%20charter%3F%20That%20is%20the%20multimillion-dollar%20question.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20expenses%20and%20headaches%20of%20owning%20a%20plane%20have%20some%20uber-wealthy%20turning%20to%20charter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EQi%20at%20the%20jet%20charter%20company%20said%20she%20doesn't%20think%20it%20makes%20financial%20sense%20to%20own%20an%20aircraft%20unless%20you%20fly%20more%20than%20350%20hours%20a%20year%2C%20want%20a%20completely%20personalized%20jet%20with%20a%20toothbrush%20and%20a%20set%20of%20fresh%20clothes%20on%20board%2C%20or%20need%20it%20at%20a%20moment's%20notice.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThrough%20charter%20companies%20like%20VistaJet%2C%20members%20can%20buy%20a%20certain%20number%20of%20flying%20hours%20a%20year%2C%20while%20%3Ca%20href%