%20a%20dip%20to%20buy.%20If%20you%20missed%20the%20April%20plunge%2C%20you%20might%20still%20be%20doing%20so.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20necessarily%20a%20bad%20approach.%20Goldman%20Sachs%20said%20this%20week%20that%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-outlook-sp500-prediction-correction-tariffs-economy-goldman-sachs-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Echance%20of%20a%20stock-market%20pullback%20has%20jumped%3C%2Fa%3E.%20In%20fact%2C%20stocks%20are%20so%20expensive%20that%20Vanguard%20said%20this%20mont%20that%20its%20ideal%20portfolio%20over%20the%20next%2010%20years%20is%20a%20very%20conservative%20allocation%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finvesting-advice-60-40-portfolio-vanguard-stock-vs-bond-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E70%25%20bonds%20and%2030%25%20stocks%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20cheaper%20the%20entry%20point%2C%20the%20better%20the%20returns.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20timing%20the%20market%20is%20tricky%20and%20something%20market%20pros%20usually%20advise%20against%20trying.%20No%20one%20knows%20how%20long%20a%20bull%20rally%20can%20go%20or%20how%20long%20an%20eventual%20pullback%20will%20last.%20That's%20why%20the%20best%20course%20of%20action%20is%20probably%20to%20dollar-cost-average%2C%20continuing%20to%20put%20money%20into%20the%20market%20at%20set%20intervals%2C%20whether%20the%20market%20is%20up%20or%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20if%20you%20are%20resolved%20to%20waiting%20for%20a%20significant%20decline%20to%20enter%20the%20market%2C%20it's%20a%20good%20idea%20to%20have%20a%20plan%20set%20in%20place%20before%20that%20moment%20arrives.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225337db50-0f79-441d-abe3-8e280f498446%5C%22%3EWhen%20and%20what%20to%20buy%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20bear%20markets%20in%20recent%20years%20have%20been%20short-lived%2C%20the%20average%20bear%20market%20going%20back%20to%201932%20has%20seen%20a%2035.1%25%20drawdown%20that%20lasts%20a%20year%20and%20a%20half%2C%20according%20to%20investment%20bank%20Stifel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20take%20it%20slow%2C%20says%20brokerage%20firm%20Charles%20Schwab.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BInstead%20of%20going%20all%20in%20at%20once%2C%20one%20might%20consider%20buying%20small%20chunks%20at%20a%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20Charles%20Schwab%20said%20in%20an%20August%206%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20not%20too%20slow%2C%20said%20Hank%20Smith%2C%20the%20director%20and%20head%20of%20investment%20strategy%20at%20Haverford%20Trust.%20There's%20no%20way%20to%20tell%20when%20the%20bottom%20is%20in%2C%20so%20you%20want%20to%20start%20taking%20advantage%20of%20the%20pullback%20once%20it%20hits%2010%25%20correction%20territory%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20may%20hurt%20if%20the%20market%20ends%20up%20falling%20further%20than%2010%25%2C%20Smith%20said%2C%20but%20being%20indecisive%20about%20when%20to%20get%20in%20can%20result%20in%20missed%20opportunities.%20Remember%20the%2019.9%25%20decline%20in%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20from%20February%20to%20April%3F%20The%20pain%20was%20over%20in%20the%20blink%20of%20an%20eye%2C%20with%20the%20index%20back%20at%20all-time%20highs%20before%20the%20end%20of%20June%20%E2%80%94%20and%20the%20rally%20has%20been%20furious%2C%20with%20the%20market%20up%2030%25%20since%20April%20lows.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20if%20the%20market%20does%20continue%20to%20drop%2C%20it's%20time%20to%20get%20even%20more%20aggressive%2C%20Smith%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLet's%20say%20that%20correction%20morphs%20into%20a%20bear%20market%20of%2020%25%2C%20and%20now%20you're%20kicking%20yourself%20that%20you%20put%20any%20in%20at%20down%2010%25.%20You%20can't%20do%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20Smith%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BYou%20have%20to%20say%2C%20'Ok%2C%20this%20is%20another%20opportunity%20to%20tranche%20in%20again%2C'%20and%20probably%20with%20more%20than%20you%20did%20at%20down%2010%25.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20areas%20of%20the%20market%20to%20buy%2C%20it's%20difficult%20to%20know%20which%20sectors%20and%20themes%20will%20get%20beaten%20up%20the%20most.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Schwab%20said%20it's%20good%20to%20take%20a%20diversified%20approach%20and%20start%20buying%20all%20corners%20of%20the%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BInterestingly%20enough%2C%20traders%20can%20diversify%20their%20portfolios%20with%20as%20few%20as%2012%20stocks%2C%20targeting%20stocks%20in%20all%20major%20sectors%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20firm%20said.%20%26quot%3BAlthough%20diversification%20doesn't%20eliminate%20the%20risk%20of%20experiencing%20investment%20losses%2C%20it%20can%20help%20increase%20the%20chances%20of%20capturing%20better-performing%20assets%20and%20avoid%20the%20risk%20of%20losing%20overall%20portfolio%20value%20to%20any%20single%20business%2C%20industry%2C%20or%20sector.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EQuality%20dividend%20stocks%20can%20also%20provide%20a%20good%20buffer%20to%20market%20losses%2C%20Merrill%20and%20Bank%20of%20America%20Private%20Bank%20said%20in%20a%202024%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESmith%20said%20that%20economically%20sensitive%20sectors%20usually%20make%20for%20some%20of%20the%20best%20opportunities%20coming%20out%20of%20a%20recessionary%20bear%20market%2C%20as%20they%20dip%20during%20downturns%20and%20rebound%20when%20the%20economy%20recovers.%20Funds%20like%20the%20Fidelity%20MSCI%20Consumer%20Discretionary%20Index%20ETF%20(FDIS)%20and%20the%20Invesco%20Dorsey%20Wright%20Consumer%20Cyclicals%20Momentum%20ETF%20(PEZ)%20offer%20exposure%20to%20cyclical%20stocks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20he%20also%20said%20large-cap%20tech%20stocks%20are%20likely%20to%20drop%20the%20most%20because%20of%20how%20high%20their%20valuations%20are.%20If%20that's%20the%20case%2C%20it%20will%20likely%20be%20a%20good%20chance%20to%20add%20exposure%20to%20them%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat's%20very%20common%20in%20high-growth%20stocks%20to%20have%20big%20sell-offs%20in%20what%20is%20a%20longer-term%20bull%20trend%2C%26quot%3B%