r%20from%20pleasant.%20%E2%80%9CWhile%20removing%20a%20hive%20frame%2C%20bees%20stung%20me%20in%20the%20eyes%2C%20leaving%20them%20badly%20swollen%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20happened%20because%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20understand%20bee%20behaviour%20at%20the%20time.%20But%20my%20passion%20kept%20me%20going.%20Instead%20of%20being%20scared%2C%20I%20chose%20to%20learn%20more%20about%20how%20bees%20behave.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20removing%20the%20frame%20from%20the%20box%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20important%20to%20do%20it%20gently%20to%20avoid%20shocking%20the%20bees.%20Also%2C%20avoid%20wearing%20perfumes%2C%20aromatic%20hair%20oils%2C%20or%20black%20clothing%2C%20as%20these%20can%20irritate%20them.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20continuing%20his%20teaching%20job%2C%20Jagpal%20began%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F277897%2Fgujarat-couple-organic-chemical-free-farming-beekeping-svadya-raw-honey%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epractising%20beekeeping%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20side.%20After%20mastering%20the%20nuances%20of%20the%20trade%2C%20he%20decided%20to%20quit%20teaching%20in%202007%20to%20devote%20himself%20fully%20to%20beekeeping.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EEmpowering%20over%20500%20fellow%20farmers%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJagpal%20raises%20the%20Apis%20mellifera%20variety%20of%20honey%20bees.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20variety%20offers%20high%20production%20and%20boosts%20pollination.%20During%20the%20flowering%20season%2C%20honey%20can%20be%20harvested%20within%20just%2010%20days.%20On%20average%2C%20I%20get%20around%2040%20kg%20of%20honey%20per%20box%20annually%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20informs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12