zon-2-1754921606-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-485007%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20spirit%20of%20optimism%20and%20determination%20rang%20through%20his%20words%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20the%20people%20of%20India%2C%20whose%20representatives%20we%20are%2C%20we%20make%20an%20appeal%20to%20join%20us%20with%20faith%20and%20confidence%20in%20this%20great%20adventure.%20This%20is%20no%20time%20for%20petty%20and%20destructive%20criticism%2C%20no%20time%20for%20ill-will%20or%20blaming%20others.%20We%20have%20to%20build%20the%20noble%20mansion%20of%20free%20India%20where%20all%20her%20children%20may%20dwell.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20appointed%20day%20has%20come-the%20day%20appointed%20by%20destiny-and%20India%20stands%20forth%20again%2C%20after%20long%20slumber%20and%20struggle%2C%20awake%2C%20vital%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F259714%2Fwest-bengal-history-woman-bela-mitra-brave-india-freedom-struggle-british-raj%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efree%20and%20independent%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20past%20clings%20on%20to%20us%20still%20in%20some%20measure%2C%20and%20we%20have%20to%20do%20much%20before%20we%20redeem%20the%20pledges%20we%20have%20so%20often%20taken.%20Yet%20the%20turning-point%20is%20past%2C%20and%20history%20begins%20anew%20for%20us%2C%20the%20history%20which%20we%20shall%20live%20and%20act%2C%20and%20others%20will%20write%20about.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20a%20fateful%20moment%20for%20us%20in%20India%2C%20for%20all%20Asia%20and%20for%20the%20world.%20A%20new%20star%20rises%2C%20the%20star%20of%20freedom%20in%20the%20East%2C%20a%20new%20hope%20comes%20into%20being%2C%20a%20vision%20long%20cherished%20materialises.%20May%20the%20star%20never%20set%20and%20that%20hope%20never%20be%20betrayed!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20rejoice%20in%20that%20freedom%2C%20even%20though%