but%20not%20only%20we%20but%20succeeding%20generations%20will%20remember%20this%20message%20and%20bear%20the%20imprint%20in%20their%20hearts%20of%20this%20great%20son%20of%20India%2C%20magnificent%20in%20his%20faith%20and%20strength%20and%20courage%20and%20humility.%20We%20shall%20never%20allow%20that%20torch%20of%20freedom%20to%20be%20blown%20out%2C%20however%20high%20the%20wind%20or%20stormy%20the%20tempest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOur%20next%20thoughts%20must%20be%20of%20the%20unknown%20volunteers%20and%20soldiers%20of%20freedom%20who%2C%20without%20praise%20or%20reward%2C%20have%20served%20India%20even%20unto%20death.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20think%20also%20of%20our%20brothers%20and%20sisters%20who%20have%20been%20cut%20off%20from%20us%20by%20political%20boundaries%20and%20who%2C%20unhappily%2C%20cannot%20share%20at%20present%20in%20the%20freedom%20that%20has%20come.%20They%20are%20of%20us%20and%20will%20remain%20of%20us%2C%20whatever%20may%20happen%2C%20and%20we%20shall%20be%20sharers%20in%20their%20good%20or%20ill%20fortune%20alike.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20future%20beckons%20to%20us.%20Whither%20do%20we%20go%20and%20what%20shall%20be%20our%20endeavour%3F%20To%20bring%20freedom%20and%20opportunity%20to%20the%20common%20man%2C%20to%20the%20peasants%20and%20workers%20of%20India%3B%20to%20fight%20and%20end%20poverty%20and%20ignorance%20and%20disease%3B%20to%20build%20up%20a%20prosperous%2C%20democratic%20and%20progressive%20nation%2C%20and%20to%20create%20social%2C%20economic%20and%20political%20institutions%20which%20will%20ensure%20justice%20and%20fullness%20of%20life%20to%20every%20man%20and%20woman.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2F5_11zon-2-1754922288.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22India%20remains%20one%20of%20the%20most%20diverse%20nations