2520quality.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecostliest%20mangoes%20%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%93%20Miyazaki!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20rare%20mango%20is%20native%20to%20Miyazaki%20city%20in%20Japan.%20It%20has%20a%20violet-red%20colour%20and%20is%20comparatively%20sweeter%2C%20juicier%2C%20and%20larger%20than%20other%20mango%20varieties%2C%20including%20the%20famous%20Alphonso%20mangoes.%20I%20was%20so%20fascinated%20by%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20fruit%20has%20an%20unusual%20appearance%20like%20an%20egg%2C%20which%20is%20why%20it%20is%20also%20known%20as%20the%20%E2%80%98Eggs%20of%20Sun.%E2%80%99%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESurprisingly%2C%20these%20mangoes%20are%20sold%20at%20Rs%202.5%20lakh%20per%20kg%20in%20the%20international%20market.%20Subrat%20cites%20their%20medicinal%20properties%20for%20their%20exorbitant%20price.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Fpmc%2Farticles%2FPMC8448164%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E2021%20research%20%3C%2Fa%3Earticle%20points%20out%20that%20these%20mangoes%20%E2%80%93%C2%A0%20botanically%20classified%20as%20Mangifera%20Indica%20%E2%80%93%20have%20anti-cancer%2C%20anti-inflammatory%2C%20antimicrobial%2C%20antioxidant%2C%20and%20immunomodulatory%20properties.%20Its%20consumption%20may%20potentially%20be%20beneficial%20in%20breast%20cancer%20management.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FSubrat-Nath-5-1715319960.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Subrat%20grows%20rare%20plants%20like%20Hydrangea%20and%20world's%20costiliest%20Miyazaki%20mangoes.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%